01:35:15.608 --> 01:35:17.351
Ruby...

01:35:17.443 --> 01:35:21.986
'A source of... little visible delight,

01:35:23.157 --> 01:35:26.074
but... necessary, '

01:35:29.497 --> 01:35:32.616
I like that.

01:35:59.527 --> 01:36:03.571
I'm a Confederate soldier...
on furlough.

01:36:03.656 --> 01:36:06.740
I need shelter... and food.

01:36:17.461 --> 01:36:19.750
I've got a rifle.

01:36:20.673 --> 01:36:22.547
Fair enough.

01:36:23.884 --> 01:36:26.340
I have some beans and corn pone.

01:36:26.429 --> 01:36:28.587
All I got.

01:36:35.729 --> 01:36:38.018
Thank you.
I'm alone here,

01:36:38.107 --> 01:36:40.645
as you can see, with my baby.

01:36:40.860 --> 01:36:43.481
I need to believe you mean no harm.

01:36:47.241 --> 01:36:49.068
No.

01:36:49.160 --> 01:36:51.366
I don't want it.

01:36:51.454 --> 01:36:55.119
If I had my way, they'd take metal
altogether out of this world.

01:36:55.207 --> 01:36:57.663
Every blade, every gun.

01:37:12.475 --> 01:37:14.348
It's all right.

01:37:14.435 --> 01:37:17.436
You're burnin' up, little man.

01:37:33.913 --> 01:37:35.952
Is your baby sick?

01:37:38.918 --> 01:37:44.160
My man's dead. Took his wound
at Gettysburg and never saw his boy.

01:37:44.256 --> 01:37:45.454
I'm sorry.

01:37:45.549 --> 01:37:49.464
It's pretty much what you'll get
if you knock on any door of this war.

01:37:49.553 --> 01:37:52.340
Man dead, woman left.

01:37:56.769 --> 01:37:58.512
It's mean food, but it's hot.

01:37:58.604 --> 01:38:02.388
There's been no huntin' on the road,
just cress and roots.

01:38:02.483 --> 01:38:05.519
I need to try and feed this man.

01:38:05.611 --> 01:38:09.443
Shh. You gotta eat somethin', baby.

01:38:22.962 --> 01:38:25.535
He won't feed.

01:38:25.631 --> 01:38:29.130
I'm Inman, by the way.
That's my name.

01:38:30.636 --> 01:38:32.712
I'm Sara.

01:38:35.641 --> 01:38:38.677
My baby's Ethan.

01:38:38.769 --> 01:38:40.180
Glad to know you both.

01:38:53.159 --> 01:38:56.278
You look about his size.

01:38:56.370 --> 01:38:59.620
He was another man
straight up and down.

01:38:59.707 --> 01:39:01.699
Thank you.

01:39:28.611 --> 01:39:30.319
Everything fit?

01:39:31.947 --> 01:39:34.154
These boots are good boots.

01:39:41.332 --> 01:39:43.823
Well, I'll say good night, then.

01:39:45.586 --> 01:39:47.579
Good night.

