Merry Christmas, darlin'.
Don't sleep here,

01:45:04.905 --> 01:45:08.025
We won't,
It's dangerous, Don't sleep here.

01:45:08.117 --> 01:45:12.280
Oh, it's bitter.
They could stop one night.

01:45:12.371 --> 01:45:14.945
They stop one night,
they're gonna wanna stop two.

01:45:15.040 --> 01:45:17.413
I'll be all right.
This coat's warm.

01:45:17.501 --> 01:45:20.288
What about next Sunday?
It'll be New Year.

01:45:20.379 --> 01:45:23.499
Maybe.
Gonna be a better one than 1864,

01:45:23.591 --> 01:45:27.540
This war's over in a month,
That's what he said a month ago.

01:45:27.636 --> 01:45:30.210
It started off bein' over in a month.

01:45:30.306 --> 01:45:32.927
Night, Miss Sally,
Merry Christmas,

01:45:33.017 --> 01:45:35.768
Night, Miss Ruby.
Night.

01:45:37.021 --> 01:45:38.301
Night, ma'am.
Night.

01:45:38.397 --> 01:45:40.853
You're stayin' with us tonight, Sally,

01:45:40.941 --> 01:45:43.646
That's my Ruby.
She's an original.

01:45:46.697 --> 01:45:52.071
