Take the chickens. They're all I got.

01:47:46.525 --> 01:47:48.565
Says she's only got chickens.

01:47:48.652 --> 01:47:52.187
You lyin' Southern trash.

01:47:52.865 --> 01:47:54.941
We're hungry.

01:47:55.034 --> 01:47:56.409
We got all day.

01:47:57.411 --> 01:48:00.365
See, those birds
won't get you through the winter.

01:48:00.456 --> 01:48:02.080
