Take me inside.
We'll do whatever you want.

01:48:58.472 --> 01:49:03.134
Take my baby inside.
Let's all go inside. Please.

01:49:03.227 --> 01:49:06.098
Please. Please.

01:49:06.188 --> 01:49:09.355
You take that hog.
I'm as good as dead.

01:49:09.442 --> 01:49:12.727
Take that hog 'cause I'm as good as dead.

